@node ANCES "Ancestral Memories"

@{b}Ancestral Memories@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(R) / PT(R)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 2UUU
Artist  = William Donohoe

Text(PT): Look at the top seven cards of your deck. Put two of them into
          your hand and the rest into your discard pile.

Text(MI): Look at the top seven cards of your library. Put two of those
          cards into your hand and the rest into your graveyard.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Even the ancient storytellers proclaimed Zhalfir to be
               dominant over all Jamuraa. Kaervek's invasion shocked
               us all." -Hakim, Loreweaver@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node AZIMA "Azimaet Drake"

@{b}Azimaet Drake@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(C)
Type    = Summon Drake (1/3)
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Gerry Grace

Text(MI): Flying.
          <U>: +1/+0 until end of turn. You cannot spend more than <U> in
          this way each turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}"A vizier's dish, best served drenched in honey and
               almonds." -Suq'Ata royal recipe@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node BAYFA "Bay Falcon"

@{b}Bay Falcon@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(C)
Type    = Summon Falcon (1/1)
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Una Fricker

Text(MI): Flying.
          Attacking does not cause Bay Falcon to tap.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Wear the falcon's feathers in your hair-be fast as
               the falcon, bright as the Sun." -"Rise on Wings,"
               Zhalfirin song@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node BAZAA "Bazaar of Wonders"

@{b}Bazaar of Wonders@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Enchant World
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Liz Danforth

Text(MI): When Bazaar of Wonders comes into play, remove all cards in all
          graveyards from the game. Whenever a spell is played, counter it
          if a card with the same name is in play or in any graveyard.@{ui}

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BAZWO}

@endnode
@node CERUL "Cerulean Wyvern"

@{b}Cerulean Wyvern@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(U)
Type    = Summon Wyvern (3/3)
Cost    = 4U
Artist  = Gerry Grace

Text(MI): Flying, protection from green.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Once, a Quirion asked why I was so cautious when
