@node ENERG "Energy Vortex"

@{b}Energy Vortex@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Tom Wanerstrand

Text(MI): When you play Energy Vortex, choose target opponent. At the
          beginning of your upkeep, remove all energy counters from Energy
          Vortex. During chosen opponent's upkeep, he or she pays <1> for
          each energy counter on Energy Vortex, or it deals 3 damage to him
          or her.
          <X>: Put X energy counters on Energy Vortex. Use this ability
          only during your upkeep.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_E.guide/ENVOR}

@endnode
